    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CODE ENTRY -->
<div id="s-code" class="screen">
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">RPM<span>.</span>SG</div>
    <div class="ntag">Athlete Intake</div>
    <button class="btn bo bsm" data-action="show" data-target="s-land">← Back</button>
  </nav>
  <div class="cw">
    <div class="box">
      <div class="tag">Step 1 of 2</div>
      <h2>Enter Your Team Code</h2>
      <p>Your coach provided a team code. Enter it below to find your name on the roster.</p>
      <p style="font-size:12px;color:var(--mid);margin-top:-8px">⏱ Takes 10–12 minutes. Must be completed in one sitting — do not close or refresh the page.</p>
      <div class="fld"><label>Team Code</label><input type="text" id="inp-code" placeholder="Enter your team code"></div>
      <div class="err" id="code-err">Invalid code. Check with your coach and try again.</div>
      <button class="btn bp bfw" id="btn-valcode" data-action="valCode">Find My Team →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- NAME SELECT -->
<div id="s-name" class="screen">
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">RPM<span>.</span>SG</div>
    <div class="ntag">Athlete Intake</div>
    <button class="btn bo bsm" data-action="show" data-target="s-code">← Back</button>
  </nav>
  <div class="cw" style="align-items:flex-start;padding-top:40px">
    <div class="box" style="max-width:560px">
      <div class="tag">Step 2 of 2</div>
      <h2>Select Your Name</h2>
      <p id="name-team-label">Find your name below and tap it to continue.</p>
      <div id="name-roster-grid" class="rg" style="margin-top:16px"></div>
      <div style="margin-top:14px;font-size:12px;color:var(--mid)" id="name-not-found-msg" style="display:none">
        Don't see your name? Your coach needs to add you to the roster before you can begin.
      </div>
      <div class="err" id="name-err" style="margin-top:12px">Please select your name to continue.</div>
      <button class="btn bp bfw" id="btn-selname" onclick="confirmName()" style="margin-top:16px;opacity:.4;pointer-events:none">This is me →</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


<!-- CONSENT -->
<div id="s-consent" class="screen">
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">RPM<span>.</span>SG</div>
    <div class="ntag">Before You Begin</div>
    <button class="btn bo bsm" data-action="show" data-target="s-code">← Back</button>
  </nav>
  <div class="cw">
    <div class="box" style="max-width:520px">
      <div style="background:rgba(29,143,90,.12);border:1px solid rgba(29,143,90,.3);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 16px;margin-bottom:20px;font-size:13px">
        ✓ Joined as <strong id="consent-name">—</strong> &nbsp;·&nbsp; Team: <strong id="consent-team">—</strong>
      </div>
      <div class="tag">Confidentiality &amp; Consent</div>
      <h2>Before You Begin</h2>
      <p>Please read the following carefully before starting your assessment.</p>
      <div class="consent-box">
        <p>Your responses to this assessment are <strong style="color:var(--w)">confidential</strong>.<br><br>Your <strong style="color:var(--w)">Panic Cycle</strong> answers will only be seen by your RPM practitioner — never by your coaches.<br><br>Your <strong style="color:var(--w)">Social Map</strong> answers will only be used in anonymous team-level reports. Your individual responses will never be shared with your coaches.<br><br>Your data is stored securely and permanently deleted two years after your program season ends. You may request deletion at any time.<br><br>For full details see our <a data-action="openPrivacy" style="color:var(--gl);text-decoration:underline;cursor:pointer">Privacy Policy</a>.</p>
