        <span>I have read and understood how my data will be used, and I consent to my responses being collected and stored as described above.</span>
      </label>
      <div class="err" id="consent-err">Please check the box above to confirm your consent before continuing.</div>
      <button class="btn bp bfw" id="consent-btn" data-action="proceedFromConsent" style="opacity:.4;pointer-events:none">Begin Assessment &rarr;</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- INTAKE -->
<div id="s-intake" class="screen">
  <nav>
    <div class="logo">RPM<span>.</span>SG</div>
    <div class="ntag" id="ilbl">Panic Cycle Assessment</div>
    <div style="font-size:11px;color:var(--mid)" id="iprog"></div>
  </nav>
  <div class="il">
    <div class="sb">
      <div class="sbsec">Part 1 — Panic Cycle</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc1"><span class="sbd"></span>Trigger Situation</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc2"><span class="sbd"></span>First Signal</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc3"><span class="sbd"></span>Emotions</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc4"><span class="sbd"></span>Inner Voice</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc5"><span class="sbd"></span>Identity Phrase</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc6"><span class="sbd"></span>Body Response</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc7"><span class="sbd"></span>Reaction</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc8"><span class="sbd"></span>Behavior</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc9"><span class="sbd"></span>Your Pattern</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc10"><span class="sbd"></span>Outcome</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-pc11"><span class="sbd"></span>Aftermath</div>
      <div class="sbsec">Part 2 — Social Map</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm1"><span class="sbd"></span>Trust</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm2"><span class="sbd"></span>Communication</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm3"><span class="sbd"></span>Safety</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm4"><span class="sbd"></span>Positive Influence</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm5"><span class="sbd"></span>Effectiveness</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm6"><span class="sbd"></span>Decision Trust</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm7"><span class="sbd"></span>Understanding</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm8"><span class="sbd"></span>Most Interaction</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm9"><span class="sbd"></span>Positive Environment</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm10"><span class="sbd"></span>Least Connected</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm11"><span class="sbd"></span>Least Interaction</div>
      <div class="sbi" id="sb-sm12"><span class="sbd"></span>Hard to Communicate</div>
    </div>
    <div class="im" id="imain">

      <div class="brk on" id="brk-start">
        <div class="bico">🧠</div>
        <h2>Part 1: Your Panic Cycle</h2>
        <p>These questions map how pressure shows up for you — your triggers, body response, and automatic reactions. No wrong answers.</p>
        <button class="btn bp" data-action="startPC">Let's Begin →</button>
      </div>

      <div class="brk" id="brk-social">
        <div class="bico">🔗</div>
        <h2>Part 2: Team Social Map</h2>
        <p>Now we map your team's relational dynamics. Select up to 2 teammates per question. Responses are fully confidential.</p>
        <button class="btn bp" data-action="startSM">Continue →</button>
      </div>

      <div class="qb" id="q-pc1">
        <div class="pm"><div class="pml">Question 1 of 23</div><div class="pt"><div class="pf" style="width:4%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="qmeta">Panic Cycle — Trigger</div>
        <div class="qt">What type of situation most often starts your cycle?</div>
        <div class="qs">Select one.</div>
        <div class="choices" id="c-pc1">
          <div class="choice" data-action="single" data-key="pc1"><span class="chk"></span>Making a visible mistake in a game</div>
          <div class="choice" data-action="single" data-key="pc1"><span class="chk"></span>Underperforming compared to expectations</div>
          <div class="choice" data-action="single" data-key="pc1"><span class="chk"></span>Conflict or tension with a teammate or coach</div>
          <div class="choice" data-action="single" data-key="pc1"><span class="chk"></span>Fear of losing my starting position or playing time</div>
          <div class="choice" data-action="single" data-key="pc1"><span class="chk"></span>High-pressure moments (playoffs, tryouts, big games)</div>
