      <div class="qb" id="q-pc3">
        <div class="pm"><div class="pml">Question 3 of 23</div><div class="pt"><div class="pf" style="width:13%"></div></div></div>
        <div class="qmeta">Panic Cycle — Emotions</div>
        <div class="qt">Which emotions feel closest in those moments?</div>
        <div class="qs">Choose up to two.</div>
